Create a View for employee table to get the salary if it is <10000 mark it as 'LOW' otherwise 
'MODERATE' in separate column 'Sal_Status'. So the result of view should display the 
following details like EmpID,EmpName,Department,Salary,Sal_Status.

CREATE VIEW EmployeeSalaryView
AS
SELECT 
    EmpID,
    EmpName,
    Department,
    Salary,
    CASE 
        WHEN Salary < 10000 THEN 'LOW'
        ELSE 'MODERATE'
    END AS Sal_Status
FROM Employees;
